</P>
<P>
 * Children are encouraged to pick up and examine a collection of bird nests, 
animal bones and skins, feathers, shells, rocks, fossils and other natural 
specimens at the "Touch Table," a changing exhibit at the Children's Museum at 
La Habra. (310) 905-9793. NONA YATES 
