</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Officials have announced the completion of a flood control channel they hope 
will be a long-term solution to a problem that has plagued the Shorecliffs golf 
course. 
</P>
<P>
 Winter storms in the late '70s and early '80s washed out parts of the golf 
club and adjoining neighborhood. 
</P>
