</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 LTC Properties Inc., an Oxnard real estate investment trust with interests in 
long-term care and other health care facilities, said its third quarter and 
nine-month earnings more than doubled from a year earlier, a result of $180 
million in investments completed in the past year. 
</P>
