$1.89 million a year before. Its quarterly revenue rose 93%, to $7.78 million 
from $4.03 million. 
</P>
<P>
 For the latest nine months, LTC reported a profit of $10.9 million, while its 
revenue gained 70%, to $19.6 million. In the same period in 1993, it earned 
$4.89 million on revenue of $11.5 million. 
