<P>
REGIONAL EARNINGS: TEKELEC TURNAROUND REPORTED FOR QUARTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Tekelec, a Calabasas-based producer of switching systems for communications 
networks, said its profit for the third quarter ended Sept. 30 was $1.36 
