</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Vitesse Semiconductor Corp. of Camarillo reported its second consecutive 
profitable quarter after two years of heavy losses. 
</P>
<P>
 Vitesse, which manufactures gallium-arsenide semiconductors, posted a profit 
of $174,000 in its fiscal fourth quarter ended Sept. 30, compared to a 
year-earlier loss of $3.2 million.Revenues totaled $9.7 million in the latest 
quarter, up 21% from $8 million a year earlier. 
</P>
<P>
