 A Los Angeles company, Commonwealth Associates Inc., has acquired Westlake 
Village-based KCD Inc., maker of an over-the-counter body fat reducer, in an 
exchange of stock valued at $20 million. 
</P>
<P>
 Commonwealth will change its name to KCD Holdings Inc. and will relocate to 
