<P>
ROTTWEILER KILLS GIRL, INJURES HER MOTHER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A 5-year-old girl has died after being mauled by a 120-pound Rottweiler in her 
back yard, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
 The girl was playing with the dog, which is owned by a family friend and had 
been at the home about a week. The girl's mother also was bitten several times 
as she tried to stop the attack Sunday. She was in fair condition. 
</P>
