<TEXT>
<P>
 Disneyland Woos Latinos: Disneyland has been continually working to capture a 
larger share of Southern California's large and growing Latino market. 
</P>
<P>
 To further that goal, the park today is going to be the site of a private 
taping of a Christmas television special featuring well-known Latino 
artists.The special is slated to be shown next month on the Univision 
Spanish-language television network. 
</P>
