WHAT'S THE DEAL: BODY WATCH; WHAT TO DO ABOUT UNRULY EYEBROWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KATHLEEN DOHENY 
</P>
</BYLINE>
