<HEADLINE>
<P>
FREEWAY SPEEDING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I have a comment about the speed on the Ventura Freeway. 
</P>
<P>
 People are driving at 80-90 m.p.h. and tailgating, and nobody uses their turn 
signals. They go from the fast lane up to the next off-ramp and almost collide 
into you. I think people should slow down or they should use their signals and 
be more courteous. 
</P>
<P>
 When the gas crunch comes and gas is $3 a gallon, these people in their Ford 
Explorers and big 4x4 trucks are going to be sorry. 
</P>
<P>
 JOSEPH LIVIO 
</P>
<P>
 Simi Valley 
</P>
</TEXT>
