</P>
<P>
 *"That is your wife you kissed, isn't it?" 
</P>
<P>
 -- First question asked of Orange's Dick Hill after he won his 200th game as 
an Orange County coach. 
</P>
<P>
 * "We drew first blood." 
</P>
<P>
