<TEXT>
<P>
 Gabriel's concert -- In Monday's review of Juan Gabriel's concert at Universal 
Amphitheatre, his accompanying mariachi group was misidentified. It was 
Mariachi Arriba Juarez. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
