<TEXT>
<P>
 "Nutcracker" company -- In a Monday item about upcoming productions of "The 
Nutcracker," the Los Angeles Classical Ballet was misidentified. In addition to 
its dates in Long Beach, the troupe will perform Dec. 22-24 at the Pasadena 
Civic Auditorium. 
</P>
</TEXT>
